As of August 2025, USDC has grown significantly:Market Cap: Over $30 billion, making it one of the largest stablecoins alongside Tether (USDT).
Transaction Volume: USDC facilitates billions in monthly transactions across blockchains, with Ethereum and Solana leading in activity.
Adoption: Supported by over 200 platforms, including major exchanges (Coinbase, Binance) and payment processors (Stripe, PayPal).

